'''Raiths''' were giant [[Color/Legends|black]] [[Rodent/Legends|rodents]] native to the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] [[Yavin 8/Legends|Yavin 8]]. They had two sharp [[Tooth/Legends|teeth]] on the top and bottom of their mouths which they used to bite with impressive force. Raiths were also distinguished by their thick, armored green tails. They preyed on young [[Melodie]]s though they were in turn hunted by the giant [[Bird/Legends|avian]] [[avril]]s.

During their trip to Yavin 8, Jedi trainees [[Anakin Solo]], [[Tahiri Veila]], and [[Lyric]] encountered a number of raiths.

